definitions.definition: Characterized by strong drum-beats and distorted guitars.
Having the emotional or social characteristics associated with metal music ; brash, bold, frank, unyielding, etc.

main_definition: ( music ) Characterized by strong drum-beats and distorted guitars. [1970s and after]
